    Quiz Application with Timer and Animations
This project is a simple Quiz Application built using HTML, CSS, and jQuery. The application includes the following features:

A set of questions displayed one at a time.
Timer functionality for each question.
Star rating system that appears after a user interacts with the options for a question.
Smooth animations for transitioning between questions and showing elements.

## Features:

- Question Navigation:
Only one question is displayed at a time.
After answering a question or when the timer ends, the next question is displayed with a sliding animation.


- Timer:
A 10-second countdown timer for each question.
When the timer runs out, the quiz automatically transitions to the next question.
Interactive 


- Star Rating:
Stars for rating appear only after an option is selected for the current question.
The star rating is reset when moving to the next question.


- Smooth Animations:
Questions slide in and out for a better user experience.
Stars fade in dynamically when triggered.



## Technologies Used

- HTML: For structuring the quiz layout and elements.
- CSS: For styling the quiz application and creating a visually appealing interface.
- jQuery: For adding interactivity, handling animations, and controlling the timer and transitions between questions.


## How to Use
Download or Clone the Repository:
bash
Copy
Edit
git clone https://github.com/your-username/quiz-app.git
Open the Application:

Navigate to the folder where the project is saved.
Open the index.html file in any modern web browser.
Interact with the Quiz:

Answer each question by clicking on the buttons inside the options.
The star rating will appear after interacting with the options.
The quiz automatically transitions to the next question after the timer ends or when you answer the question.
